                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-998" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM ISAAC</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. She told me she knew nothing about it—she afterwards acknowledged pawning them at Walker's—that old <hi rend="italic">Tom</hi> had been with her, and given them to her.</p>
